      • enforceBedtime

        public java.lang.String enforceBedtime()
        Every household can enforce the bedtime as its child. For this method, check if it is past the household's instance of child's bedtime by comparing it to the time variable If it's past the child's bedtime, return "go to bed!" Otherwise, return "I guess you can watch a little more tv"
        Returns:
        string depending on if it's past the child's bedtime
